  "description": "<h2>Job Purpose</h2><p>The HR Generalist supports the company’s\npeople and compliance needs by managing core HR functions, with a strong focus\non foreign manpower administration, employee relations, and recruitment. </p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><p>• Manage employee lifecycle matters for\nlocal and foreign staff<br />\n• Prepare and review employment contracts and HR documentation<br />\n• Support recruitment and manpower planning<br />\n• Handle work pass applications and foreign manpower compliance<br />\n• Support employee relations and disciplinary matters<br />\n• Assist in HR policy implementation and compliance<br />\n• Coordinate with departments on HR related advice</p>",
